Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:36.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,今天早上很冷  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's cold this morning, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:47.07,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,很冷\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:02:00.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,严寒\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:19.81,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是时候了  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's time, Captain.
