Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你这儿在干什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你应该在楼上睡觉\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're supposed to be upstairs sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:56.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-斯坦利不断吵醒我  -原来是这样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Stanley keeps waking me up.  -Oh, I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:00.84,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你越来越重了  -胡说\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-You're getting heavy.  -Don't let her pull more than her usual nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:04.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她最多只准喝两杯水  听两个故事  杰克...\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Two stories. Two glasses of water. Jack...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你快要错过班机了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're going to miss the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好的  宝贝  听话\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}OK. Cricket, you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:11.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,跟惠勒太太上楼睡觉去\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go upstairs with Mrs. Wheeler now and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:13.98,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这次商务旅行\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When I'm on my business trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我会给斯坦利买一个小弟弟  好吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll get Stanley a little brother, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:19.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-一言为定?  -一言为定\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Will you promise?  -I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:57.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-先生  有什么吩咐吗?  -没有  谢谢你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Can I get you anything, sir?  -No, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,睡一觉吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know, if you try and get some sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.24,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,时间会过得快一点\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the flight will go a lot faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:05.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在飞机上睡不着觉  我讨厌乱流\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can never sleep on a plane. Turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:09.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-什么?  -乱流\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Pardon?  -Turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,阳光照射地面\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Solar radiation heats the earth's crust...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,热空气上升  冷空气下降\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}warm air rises, cool air descends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:18.13,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-我不喜欢乱流  -还是睡一睡吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-I don't like that.  -Oh, well, try to get some sleep anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,瑞恩博士\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Dr Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:18.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,杰克  小伙子  进来吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Jack, boy, get yourself in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你很憔悴\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Jesus, you look like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:23.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谢谢你  司令\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you very much, Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-要咖啡吗?  -好的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Want coffee?  -I think I need some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:29.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你一定不享受这次旅程\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm not going to ask you how your flight went.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,上次睡觉是什么时候?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When did you last get some sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:35.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不知道  这表还是伦敦时间\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, I don't know. This thing's still on London time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:38.88,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-加糖加奶  -加糖加奶\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Milk and sugar?  -Milk and sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:42.05,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,卡罗琳好吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How's Caroline?
