Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:48.64,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她很好  她向你致以问候\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}She's fine. She sends you her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.58,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-莎莉呢?  -他很好\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-And Sally?  -She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:54.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他有三岁了吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What is she now, three?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:58.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,五岁了  人小鬼大\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, she's a very precocious five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:01.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她说\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}She announced to Caroline...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.78,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果我们买一个小弟弟...\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I the other day that her life would be less lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:08.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她就不会那么寂寞\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}if we were to buy her a baby brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.74,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,后来她叫我们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But she decided it would be enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:13.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,给斯坦利买个弟弟\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}if we were to buy one for Stanley.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:19.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-谁是斯坦利?  -斯坦利是玩具熊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Who's Stanley?  -Ah, Stanley's a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:26.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为什么半夜赶乘飞机来这里?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What's important enough to get you on a plane in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,英国情报局两天前获得这些\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}British Intelligence obtained these pictures two days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:31.05,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,红十月号的照片\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}She's the Red October.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:35.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-红十月号是最新的台风级潜艇  -真他X的大\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-She's the latest Typhoon class.  -Big son of a bitch.
