Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:43.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-舰长叫雷米斯  -你调查过他?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Captain's name is Ramius.  -One of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:46.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我去年调查过他\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I did the bio on him last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他负责测试各级新型潜艇10年了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He's taken out the lead boat in each new sub class for 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,政治关系良好\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fairly good political connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:54.24,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,大部分舰长都是由他一手训练\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Trained most of their attack-boat skippers.
