Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:02.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,"维尔纽斯校长"\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The Vilnius schoolmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:07.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-这些是什么门?  -这些门正是问题所在\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-What are these doors?  -Those doors, sir, are the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:11.03,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不知道那是什么  英国人也不知道\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't know what they are, neither do the British.
