Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.52,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,潜艇驾驶员?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The sub driver?
