Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:15.48,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我只不过是履行职责\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I am only doing my job. It is my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:20.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,克格勃派了多少特工到我的艇上?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How many agents did the KGB put aboard my boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你的艇  舰长?  -是的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Your boat, Captain?  -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这艘潜艇属于苏联人民\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This vessel belongs to the people of the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:31.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果艇上有克格勃或者情报局的特工\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Besides, if the KGB or the GRU has agents aboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:34.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我也不知情\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I would be the last to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:40.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,启读命令吧  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I suggest we open our orders, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:43.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好的  同志\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Certainly, comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:30.68,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,红旗北军潜艇部队\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}From Commander Strategic Submarine Forces Red Banner Northern Fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:35.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们向北方  坐标54-90进发\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We are to proceed north, to grid square 5490.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:39.44,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,与雅夫级潜艇科诺瓦洛夫号会合\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and rendezvous with Alfa submarine Konovalov.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,图波列夫的艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain Tupolev's boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:46.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你认识图波列夫?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know Tupolev?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我知道他是上层人物\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I know he descends from aristocracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.11,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,也是你的门生\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and that he was your student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:53.03,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,据说他特别敬重你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's rumored he has a place in his heart for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:58.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,图波列夫只会敬重他自己\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's little room in Tupolev's heart for anyone but Tupolev.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:03.71,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,会合后  两艘潜艇一起演习\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Having made contact, we are to run a series of drills.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,图波列夫猎杀我们的潜艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tupolev will hunt us while we test our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:11.09,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们测试履带式推进器\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We are to evaluate the readiness of the caterpillar drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:16.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,然后在本月十六日返回波利尼湾\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We return to Polijarny on or about the 16th of this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰长  这是一个历史时刻\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain, This is an historic moment for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.48,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我有一个请求\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I should like to make a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-在提出请求前...  -我知道这不合规矩\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Before you proceed...  -I know it's not protocol...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但请让我\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but would you permit me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:28.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,向船员公布任务\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}post our orders and inform the crew of our mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:58.06,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我要去一个地方  你不能同行\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Where I am going, you can not follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:29.34,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,彼得罗夫医生  立刻来舰长室\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Dr Petrov, report to my cabin immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:32.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这里发生了意外\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's been a dreadful accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:42.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,4号码头  美军船坞  马里兰州
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,接着!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:20.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,下面没有支船架  快点动手\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Listen to me. There's no cradle underneath it. Get it over。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:25.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别那么固执  上来帮我吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Relax! Stop being an old maid. You want to come up here and do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:32.98,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,瑞恩  谁让你进来的?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ryan! Who let you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:37.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们叫你来砌模型?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Have they got you playing with models now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:43.49,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,该死的  叫他慢下来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Damn it, Phil! Tell them to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:49.08,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这不是模型  这是深潜救助艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's not a model. It's a DSRV. Rescue sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.71,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我知道这是什么  我原来见过一艘\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I know what it is. And I just need to see one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:52.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你拿它来做什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What are you doing with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:55.38,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,改装入坞设计\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ah, well, we're rigging it with a generic docking collar...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:58.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,它可以配合各国潜艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}so it'll mate with British, German... just about anybody's sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:01.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在24小时内赶到世界每个角落\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We can get it anywhere in the world in 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:09.52,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你的背没事吧?  -没事  有没有时间?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-How's your back?  -It's fine. Have you got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:15.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,比常规的台风级潜艇更大  这些是什么门?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's bigger than a regular Typhoon. What are these doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:18.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你真细心\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You don't miss much, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:22.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,它们比鱼雷发射管大\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Those are too big to be torpedo tubes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:25.06,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,用来发射洲际弹道导弹?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Can you launch an ICBM horizontally?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:27.12,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是的  你想问什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sure. Why would you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:32.84,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,它们是对称的  排在舰轴两边\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're symmetrical, right down the long axis of the sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.67,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,拖曳线阵列声纳呢?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How about a towed sonar array?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:38.34,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,肯定不是  太靠近螺旋桨了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Nope. Too close to the screws.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:41.64,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,怎么会...\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这可能是履带\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This could be a caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:47.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:50.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,履带驱动  磁性压水式推进器\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Uh, a caterpillar drive. Magneto-hydrodynamic propulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:52.48,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-明白吗?  -不明白\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Do you follow?  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:57.11,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,它就像水中的喷射引擎\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's like a jet engine for the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:59.76,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,靠向后的反冲推进\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Goes in the front, gets squirted out the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:02.24,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没有运动部件  所以非常的安静\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Only it's got no moving parts, so it's very, very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:04.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有多安静?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Like how quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:07.54,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们的声纳绝对发现不了它\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's doubtful our sonar would even pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,听起来像是鲸鱼游动\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And if it did, it would sound like whales humping...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:10.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,或是地壳震动\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}or a seismic anomaly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:13.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一点也不像潜艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Anything but a submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:17.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们数年前研制这种潜艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We messed with this a couple of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:21.05,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但未成功\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Couldn't make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:23.07,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们成功了?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They really built this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:24.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这不是个模型吧?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This isn't a mock-up or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:26.76,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,它今早出海了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}She put to sea this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:37.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,十二岁时  我帮爸爸建造防空洞\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When I was twelve, I helped my daddy build a bomb shelter in our basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:43.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,因为有人打算向佛罗里达州发射导弹\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}because some fool parked a dozen warheads 90 miles off the coast of Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:47.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这东西能向华盛顿和纽约  发射二百枚导弹\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This thing could park 200 warheads off Washington or New York...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.08,0:22:54.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,而且神不知鬼不觉\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and no one would know anything about it until it was all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:07.26,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-舰长  你没事吧?  -没事\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Are you all right, Captain?  -Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:11.98,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,被地上的茶水滑了一跤  竟然断送生命\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's just to die for something as petty as slipping on tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:14.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你不必自责  舰长  这是个意外\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're blaming yourself, Captain. It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:16.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,回基地后你的心情自然会平复\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You'll feel better when we put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:20.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-平复?  -嗯  回基地后  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Put in?  -Well, to base, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:22.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们不能没有政治委员\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We cannot go on without a political officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:24.32,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,医生  这是艘苏联战舰\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Doctor, this is a combat vessel of the Soviet Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:28.64,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,而我是个资深舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I'm a senior combat officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:33.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们不能为这意外撤销任务\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We do not cancel operations because of accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:39.13,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,水兵  过来  过来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Seaman, come here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.13,0:23:44.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你叫什么名字?  -副厨师洛吉诺夫\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Your name?  -Cook's Assistant, Loginov, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.76,0:23:48.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好  你和医生来当见证人\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good. I want you and the doctor to witness this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:52.04,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我要解除政治委员的导弹钥匙\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm removing the Political Officer's missile key carry on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.04,0:23:55.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,并由我来保管\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I'm keeping it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.48,0:23:59.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰长  我认为这得请示红旗舰队总司令\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain, I think we should report this to Red Fleet Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:02.13,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这恐怕不行  医生\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm afraid that's impossible, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:04.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们必须保持无线电静默\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Our orders are for strict radio silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:10.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你可以走了  -这样不太好  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-That's all, Loginov.  -This is most unnerving, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.49,0:24:14.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,发出两条钥匙\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The reason for having two missile keys...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.35,0:24:18.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,就是为了避免...\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}is so that no one man may...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.38,0:24:23.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-避免什么?  -避免一人控制导弹\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-May what?  -May arm the missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.71,0:24:25.92,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,也许我应该控制钥匙\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Perhaps I should keep the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.92,0:24:28.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谢谢你  医生  你可以走了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you. That'll be all, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.30,0:24:33.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我将会发布指令  到时候你就会明白\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When I address the crew, then you will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.31,0:24:44.32,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,彼得罗夫  我不会向中央报告你的言论\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Petrov, I will try to forget your comments when I present my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.49,0:24:47.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谢谢  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.58,0:24:58.42,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在方位310  速度12节  距离20000码\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Holding steady on 310. 12 knots at about 20,000 yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.58,0:25:03.63,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-有没有资料?  -电脑正在分析\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Have you got a make on it?  -The computer is chewing on it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:07.09,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,双螺旋桨  像是台风级潜艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Twin screws. The plant noise sounds like a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.77,0:25:16.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是艘新型潜艇  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd say we got a new boat, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.18,0:25:20.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,汤姆  最近几天总部有没有新消息?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tommy, I miss something on the boards last few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.10,0:25:23.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没有新的潜艇记录\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sub plant hasn't said anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.86,0:25:30.24,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-电脑记录了多少台风级潜艇?  -6艘\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-All right. How many Typhoons are listed?  -Six, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.41,0:25:32.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好的  称它为"台风七号"\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}OK. Call this guy Typhoon Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.45,0:25:34.49,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,靠近点开始监听\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Start a tape on him. See if we can work in a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.49,0:25:36.54,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,遵命  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.12,0:25:41.38,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,它会听到我们吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Won't he hear us?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.38,0:25:44.63,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,潜艇有听觉盲点  博蒙特\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Not if we stay in his baffles, Seaman Beaumont.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.80,0:25:48.76,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们听不见螺旋桨背后的声音\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come in behind his propeller and he's deaf as a post.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.20,0:26:20.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,声纳有新发现吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Any sonar contacts, Mr.Kamarov?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.43,0:26:23.67,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没有新发现  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No contacts, Captain. The sonar is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.83,0:26:26.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,海面有没有发现船只  鲍罗丁?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good. Do we have any surface contacts, Mr. Borodin?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.00,0:26:28.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没有任何目标\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No contacts, sir. Scope is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.34,0:26:32.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好  我要向船员说明任务\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good. Then it's time I explain our orders to the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.09,0:26:37.26,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,同志们  我是舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Comrades, this is your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.43,0:26:40.56,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我感到很荣幸\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It is an honor to speak to you today...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.73,0:26:43.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们驾驶祖国最先进的潜艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I'm honored to be sailing with you on the maiden voyage...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.25,0:26:45.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,作首次航行\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}of our motherland's most recent achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.94,0:26:50.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们将再玩一个危险游戏\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And once more, we play our dangerous game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.03,0:26:56.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,跟我们的老对手美国海军  一较高下\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A game of chess, against our old adversary the American Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.99,0:27:00.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,四十年来  你们的父亲和兄长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}For 40 years, your fathers before you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.60,0:27:04.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一直跟他们周旋\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and your older brothers played this game and played it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.38,0:27:09.76,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但现在情况转变了  我们占有优势\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But today the game is different. We have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.92,0:27:14.09,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我想起我们昔日的人造地球卫星和尤里·加加林\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It reminds me of the heady days of Sputnik and Yuri Gagarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.26,0:27:17.68,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们的火箭令世界震惊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}when the world trembled at the sound of our rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.85,0:27:21.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们的无声潜艇  也会令世界震惊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It will tremble again at the sound of our silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.52,0:27:25.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-命令:以无声推进系统潜航  -是  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The order is: Engage the silent drive.  -Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.77,0:27:29.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-水柜控制  开启外门  -外门开启\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ballast control, open outer doors.  -Yes, open outer doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.78,0:27:33.07,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,潜水官  关闭主引擎  使用履带推进\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Diving command. Engage caterpillar and secure main engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.70,0:27:39.79,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,正在开门  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Doors opening, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.95,0:27:43.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,同志们  我们的舰队也不知道我们的威力\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Comrades, our own fleet doesn't know our full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.12,0:27:46.92,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们想尽一切办法测试我们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They will do everything possible to test us,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.08,0:27:49.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们最终只会自惭形秽\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but they will only test their own embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.65,0:27:52.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们将撇下其他舰只\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We will leave our fleet behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.38,0:27:56.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,无声无息地穿过美国舰队的巡逻  穿过他们的声纳网\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We will pass through the American patrols pass their sonar nets...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.05,0:28:02.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,进入各大城市  一边听美国摇滚乐\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and lay off their largest city and listen to their rock 'n' roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.35,0:28:05.44,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一边进行导弹演习\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}while we conduct missile drills.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.69,0:28:12.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们最终只会听到我们的笑声\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When we are finished the only sound they will hear is our laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.86,0:28:19.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,然后我们驶到哈瓦那迎接阳光和友谊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}while we sail to Havana where the sun is warm and so is the comradeship.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.62,0:28:22.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,冷却系统已经启动\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Cryogenic plant coming on line, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.80,0:28:27.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,同志们  今天是大日子  我们缔造历史\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A great day, comrades. We sail into history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.92,0:28:37.38,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,启动履带式推进器\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Caterpillar engaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.47,0:28:40.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,履带式推进器已启动  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Caterpillar engaging, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.53,0:28:58.07,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-发生了什么事?  -不知道\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-What happened?  -I don't know.
