Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.16,0:42:19.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,最后  派人接触雷米斯\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The third, somebody's got to go make contact with Ramius...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.85,0:42:22.54,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,找出他的动机\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and find out what his intentions really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.71,0:42:25.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好  你何时出发?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Okay, when do you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.55,0:42:30.88,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.05,0:42:35.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,将军说得对  我只是局外人  我是个分析员而已\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The general was right. I am not field personnel. I am only an analyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.31,0:42:38.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你是最佳人选  我不能差遣他们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're perfect. I can't ask any of these characters to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.60,0:42:42.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,第一  他们不会相信  他们不会凭直觉行事\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}One, they don't believe them. Two, they wouldn't stake their reputations on a hunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.35,0:42:45.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-而你...  -可以被牺牲\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-where as you...  -Are expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.61,0:42:50.78,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,差不多\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.03,0:42:56.49,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在三天之内证实你的理论\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll give you three days to prove your theory correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.66,0:43:03.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,否则我们要消灭雷米斯  明白吗\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}After that, I have to hunt down Ramius and destroy him. Will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.85,0:43:13.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,坐标54-90  苏联雅夫级潜艇  卡华洛夫号  舰长图波列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.06,0:43:22.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,岂有此理\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mother of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.35,0:43:26.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,双引擎三分之二全速前进\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Secure the masts. All ahead two thirds. Set depth to 900 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.61,0:43:30.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-发生什么事了?  -关闭舱盖  三分之二速度下潜\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-What is it? What's happened?  -Mast secured, helm at 2/3.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.40,0:43:36.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,左转至方位205\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come left, heading 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.30,0:43:53.68,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,命令是七小时前发布的  呆在底下\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}These orders are seven bloody hours old! Sitting on the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.68,0:43:57.05,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,像个头脑混乱的小孩\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Like an addled schoolboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.22,0:44:00.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-舰长  -超速前进\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Captain?  -All ahead flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.02,0:44:06.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,问下工程师反应堆能否推动至105%\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Inquire of the engineer about going to 105% on the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.36,0:44:12.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,七小时了  整支舰队在追捕他\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Seven hours! The entire fleet is after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.04,0:44:22.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,到达900米深\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Leveling at 900 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.91,0:44:29.55,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰长  工程师说反应堆可推动至105%  但不建议这样\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain, Engineer reports 105% on the reactor is possible... but not recommended.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.14,0:44:43.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,推动至百分之一百零五\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go to 105 on the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.60,0:44:51.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-什么事? 我们去哪里?  -去杀一个朋友\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Captain, what is it? Where are we going?  -We're going to kill a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.57,0:44:56.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们去杀雷米斯\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're going to kill Ramius.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.22,0:45:20.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,从没在舰上喝过这么难喝的罗宋汤\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you like borscht, perhaps, but I've eaten better in an oiler's galley.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.97,0:45:26.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我太太对待应说  这厨子在阿富汗学烹饪?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My wife asked the waiter, "Where did this man learn to cook, Afghanistan?"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.44,0:45:30.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,然后我们去看芭蕾舞  去看那位像吉赛尔的新舞者\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So then we went on to the Bolshoi, the ballet, to see this new girl as Giselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.02,0:45:35.53,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那位新舞蹈员真是漂亮  她嫁给工厂经理...\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You remember how beautiful she was. She just married a factory manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.69,0:45:42.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,医生  有没有最新的辐射测验数据\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Excuse me, Doctor. Do you have the figures for the latest batch of radiation tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.45,0:45:44.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,现在要?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.00,0:45:48.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.33,0:45:54.13,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,上一次测验的数据也拿来吧  作个对比\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Perhaps you could bring the preceding set as well... for comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.30,0:45:57.17,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谢谢你  医生\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.86,0:46:17.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他不会这么快回来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It will take him some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.36,0:46:23.24,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在开始前  我想了解普金的死因\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Before we begin, Captain. I'd like to know exactly what happened to Putin.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.12,0:46:35.42,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-他不是真的滑倒吧  -我不喜欢你这样的语气\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-He didn't slip on his tea, did he?  -I don't think I like your tone, Slavin.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.59,0:46:37.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们在这儿\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What the hell's my tone got to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.99,0:46:40.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,身处险境\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're risking our lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.40,0:46:42.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,普金会带来麻烦\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Putin could have made complications.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.97,0:46:47.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你以为他会袖手旁观  成全我们?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Did you think he would go away and sulk while we carried out our plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.18,0:46:50.48,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他被谋杀?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you saying he was murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.48,0:46:53.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-老天  -别发牢骚\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-My God.  -Stop whining, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.94,0:46:57.82,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他就是被谋杀的  他是个混蛋\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So he was murdered. I have no problem with that. The man was a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.99,0:47:02.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-但我们应该一起做决定  -你不是指挥官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-But it is a decision we should have all made together.  -You are not in command here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.32,0:47:07.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果真相败露  船员会叛变\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If the crew finds out, we could have a mutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.54,0:47:10.54,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,艇上每一件事都会影响我们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Everything that happens on this ship affects us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.54,0:47:13.54,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,纠察长已经起了疑心\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The Master-At-Arms is already suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.71,0:47:19.34,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-现在还可以回去...  -绝不能回头\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-We could still go back.  -There'll be no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.51,0:47:25.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,启航前  我给巴度宁上将寄了封信\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Before we sailed, I dispatched a letter to Admiral Padorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.51,0:47:29.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我在信内宣布了叛变计划\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}in which I announced our intention to defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.64,0:47:35.06,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我的天  为什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In the name of God, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.23,0:47:39.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,到达新世界后  科特兹烧掉所有船\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When he reached the new world, Cortez burned his ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.07,0:47:45.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-手下只好跟他一起奋斗  -你把我们置之死地\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-As a result, his men were well motivated.  -You have signed our death warrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.74,0:47:51.41,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-巴多宁上将会派整支舰队来  -他们会追捕我们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Padorin will send the entire fleet.  -Jesus! They'll find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.58,0:47:56.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没有人会来找我们  住口吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Nobody is going to find us. That's enough, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.42,0:48:01.92,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,把潜艇交给美国是不够的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You had to do it, huh? You couldn't just turn the submarine over to the Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.09,0:48:05.84,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你还要发表政治宣言\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You had to make a political statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.01,0:48:12.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,背后隐藏着什么心态? 为何不能静静地溜走?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Or was it something deeper, Captain? Something that made you unable to slip away?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.89,0:48:19.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-是虚荣心作崇吧?  -我们为着不同的原因叛变  维克多\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Was it ego, Captain?  -We each have our reasons, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.57,0:48:24.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,收到这潜艇的蓝图后  我开始思变\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My own began the day I was handed the blueprints for this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.36,0:48:28.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这潜艇本来只有一个用途  我改变它的用途...\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A ship which had but one use. And as for the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.16,0:48:33.71,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我会负上全责\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}well, those are things that I alone must carry the burden for.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.92,0:48:40.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,安纳托利  你害怕我们的舰队  你应该害怕\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Anatoly, you're afraid of our fleet. Well, you should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.67,0:48:45.84,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我相信  我们有三分一的胜算\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Personally, I give us... one chance in three.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.18,0:48:53.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,要茶吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}More tea, anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.44,0:48:57.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不要了?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.44,0:49:00.77,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你们可以回岗位了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then you may report back to your posts.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.00,0:49:20.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,听到舰长的命令吧  散会\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You heard the captain, dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.43,0:49:30.51,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.57,0:49:48.24,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不会在他们面前反驳你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain, I would never disagree with you in front of the men, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.41,0:49:52.12,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但这次维克多说得对\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But in this case Victor was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.28,0:49:57.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-不通知莫斯科会比较好  -瓦西里\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-It would have been better if you had not informed to Moscow.  -Oh, Vasily.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.41,0:50:03.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,莫斯科不足为患  苏联海军也不难对付\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Moscow is not the worry, nor the whole Soviet Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.17,0:50:08.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我了解他们的战略  我有优势\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I know their tactics. I have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.51,0:50:15.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,美国人才叫人担心\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The worry is the Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.56,0:50:20.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,遇上适当的对手才会成功\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If we meet the right sort, this will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.94,0:50:27.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果对方性急鲁莽...\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We get some buckaroo...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.53,0:50:36.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有乱流  你不喜欢坐飞机?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Some turbulence. You don't like flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.50,0:50:40.71,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这不算是什么  5个月前的乱流那才厉害\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is nothing. You should have been here five months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.87,0:50:45.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,呕吐更是不在话下  我们在日本海遇上雹暴\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Talk about puke! We ran into a hail storm over the Sea of Japan, Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.75,0:50:50.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,机师吐在挡风玻璃上\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The pilot shot his lunch all over the windshield...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.47,0:50:53.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我往无线电吐\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I barfed on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.30,0:50:56.29,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一切倾囊而出\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Knocked it out completely, and it wasn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.29,0:50:59.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那是次重量级呕吐\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}lightweight stuff either! It was that chunky, industrial-weight puke!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.44,0:51:02.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,要不要吃一点?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You want a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.02,0:51:06.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,下次我会把你的高见记在备忘录中\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Next time you get a bright idea, just put it in a memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.36,0:51:13.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,美国企业号  北大西洋舰队  新斯科舍以东
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.70,0:51:20.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-长官  -你可以走了  中尉\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Sir.  -That will be all, Lieutenant. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.54,0:51:25.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-鹰眼那班机怎么样了?  -遇上了强风\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-That hawkeye from Weymouth Trap?  -Four wire. Caught a gust over the fantail.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.67,0:51:29.88,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-那还不算太差  -这位先生想见你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Not bad considering.  -The gentleman is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.05,0:51:33.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,查理  你说什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The gentleman? What the hell are you talking about, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.30,0:51:38.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,司令说  穿军服才不会惹人注意\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I apologize for the uniform, sir. This is Admiral Greer's idea of a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.35,0:51:41.58,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你是司令的下属?  -是的  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-You work for Jim Greer?  -That's all right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.58,0:51:44.81,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,告诉我  到底发生了什么事\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then I imagine you'll tell me what all the hubbub's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.69,0:51:52.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰长  你有时间吗?  有个东西你应该去看看\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain, you got a minute? Jonesy's got something I think you ought to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.91,0:51:59.16,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你去喝点咖啡  叫他们给我送茶来  -好的  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Martinez, get yourself a cup of coffee. Send me up some tea.  -Aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.33,0:52:02.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,舰长要一杯茶\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Messenger, get the captain a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.38,0:52:11.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,台风七号消失后  我听到歌声...\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain. Sir, the moment that sub went silent and I thought I heard singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.13,0:52:15.51,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我听到很微弱的背景声\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I heard something in the background, real faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.51,0:52:18.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,等其它潜艇离开后  我录下这些声音\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}After all those subs took off, I caught it again and got it on tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.06,0:52:24.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,用电脑过滤声带  剩下这声音\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I washed it through the computer and was able to isolate this sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.15,0:52:32.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,电脑认为  这是"岩浆移位"的声音\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The computer identified it as magma displacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.36,0:52:37.41,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这套软件本来是用来探测地震的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The SAPS software was originally written to look for seismic events.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.57,0:52:41.41,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,所以  它用地震来解释陌生的音调\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When it gets confused, it runs home to momma.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.58,0:52:44.58,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-我不知道你想说什么  -对不起\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-I'm not following you.  -Sir, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.75,0:52:47.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,以十倍速度再听听\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Listen to it at ten times speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.34,0:52:59.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-这一定是人为的声音  -对\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Now, that's got to be manmade, Captain.  -All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.85,0:53:06.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,首次发现目标是9时15分  方位269\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The first contact was at 09:15 and the bearing was 269.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.35,0:53:09.02,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,9时30分的时候  它在这里\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}At 09:30, it was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.02,0:53:11.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在11时和11时15分又在这两点发现它\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I came back to it at 11:00 and 11:15, here and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.86,0:53:14.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,苏联潜艇可以高速驶过\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Remember the dispatch we got about Russian sub skippers running...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.72,0:53:17.57,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,雷克雅内斯海脊\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the Reykjanes Ridge at high speeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.74,0:53:19.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,因为他们掌握了海底悬崖的地势\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}because they had hyper-accurate surveys of the underwater canyons...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.47,0:53:21.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们有"红航线一号"\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah, Red Route One.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.37,0:53:26.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-海底悬崖的入口是托尔双峰  -是的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-The front door to those canyons was a formation called Thor's Twins, Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.37,0:53:28.71,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,看看这个\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.64,0:53:46.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-直驱"红航线一号"  -舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Right into Red Route One.  -Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.52,0:53:50.23,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我可能疯了  但我打赌\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You may think I'm crazy, but I'll bet that...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.23,0:53:53.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这是艘新型苏联潜艇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}magma displacement was actually some new Russian sub...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.11,0:53:58.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,它驶向冰岛海岸\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and it's headed for the Iceland coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.36,0:54:01.64,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,恕我直言  钟斯\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Have I got this straight, Jonesy?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.64,0:54:04.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你不信任价值四千万的电脑说是地震\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A $40 million computer tells you you're chasing an earthquake...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.08,0:54:10.42,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你要另找答案\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but you don't believe it. And you come up with this on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.58,0:54:16.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-是的  -别紧张  我相信你\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Yes, sir.  -Relax, you've sold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.76,0:54:24.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,汤米  计划航线  赶去"红航线一号"\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tommy, I want you to plot us a speed course for the bottom end of Red Route One.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.64,0:54:27.39,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,进了海底峡谷就无法找到他们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We'll never find him in those canyons.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.39,0:54:30.15,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们先移动到潜望镜深度  但最好先通知总部\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}First take us to periscope depth. But first we'd better phone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.31,0:54:33.44,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,遵命  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Aye, aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.20,0:54:43.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,等等  钟斯\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hang on, Jonesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.75,0:54:51.83,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果我们能靠近它  你可以追踪它吗?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If I can get you close enough, can you track this sucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.00,0:54:58.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是的  我听过它的声音  它逃不掉的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes, sir. Now that I know what to listen for... I'll bag him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.59,0:55:03.18,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-继续工作  -遵命  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Carry on.  -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.35,0:55:06.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,真是荒天下之大谬\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's the craziest notion I've ever heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.66,0:55:09.98,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,整艘潜艇全体成员都想叛变?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}a serving line officer? An entire ballistic missile submarine?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.14,0:55:14.48,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,就算只是军官叛变  我也不相信\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They can't all want to defect, even if it's only the officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.65,0:55:18.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-他有什么计划?  -计划?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-What's his plan?  -His plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.36,0:55:21.82,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,苏联人连上厕所也会预先计划\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Russians don't take a dump without a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.99,0:55:24.32,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,高级军官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Senior captains don't start...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.32,0:55:26.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不会贸然冒险\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}something this dangerous without having thought the matter through.
