Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.58,1:16:18.63,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-他怎么样  -他不愿离开\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-What about him?  -He won't leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.60,1:16:31.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我见过美人鱼\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know, I've seen a mermaid once.
