Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.98,1:17:22.46,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们会探测情况\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're emerging from the route, Captain.
