Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.11,1:17:32.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,履带推进系统恢复正常工作\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The caterpillar is operational and appears to be running normally.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.37,1:17:38.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,内奸的事令船员人心惶惶\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The crew know about the saboteur and they are afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.17,1:17:44.13,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可以在适当时机利用这心态\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, that could be useful when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.47,1:17:51.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,十六小时后  会到达拉布拉多海岸\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know, we could make the Labrador Coast in 16 hours.
