Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.82,1:18:14.87,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们会不会让我住在蒙大拿州?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Do you think they will let me live in Montana?
