Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.55,1:18:30.97,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好  我会住在蒙大拿州\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good, then I will live in Montana.
