Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.10,1:18:39.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她会为我做饭\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And she will cook them for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.77,1:18:43.44,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我会买一辆小货车\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I will have a pickup truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.61,1:18:49.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可能还会买一辆旅行车\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Or possibly even a recreational vehicle...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.07,1:18:54.08,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,开着旅行车穿州过省\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and drive from state to state.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.24,1:18:58.37,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-可以这样做?  -是的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Do they let you do that?  -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.54,1:19:03.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-不必申请?  -无须申请  穿州过省\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-No papers?  -No papers. State to state.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.38,1:19:06.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好  开始转向\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All right. Commence your turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.67,1:19:15.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,冬天住在亚利桑那州\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well then... in winter, I will live in Arizona.
