Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.50,1:19:45.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-指挥室  疯狂伊凡!  -停车  保持安静\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Conn! Sonar! Crazy Ivan!  -All stop. Quick quiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.43,1:19:56.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,发生了什么  钟斯?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What's going on, Jonesy?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.66,1:19:59.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,苏联潜艇会突然急转  以探查自己是否被跟踪\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Russian captains sometimes turn suddenly to see if anyone's behind them.
