Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.56,1:20:06.23,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们要关掉所有机器\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The only thing you can do is go dead, shut everything down...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.23,1:20:08.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,销声匿迹\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and make like a hole in the water.
