Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.87,1:20:21.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果我们太近  会被卷进它的船尾\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If we're too close, we'll drift right into the back of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.50,1:20:26.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你呢  有什么心愿?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What about you? What do you look forward to?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.22,1:20:41.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我再没有这种心情\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have no such appetites.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.89,1:20:45.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,看看他们能否能听见我们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's see if he can hear us.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.44,1:20:52.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一定还有事情想做\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There must be something.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.87,1:21:04.04,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你想做什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.17,1:21:10.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我怀念小时候\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I miss the peace of fishing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.96,1:21:14.67,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,宁静地钓鱼的日子\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Like when I was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.22,1:21:22.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,四十年来  我一直航海  海上的战争\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}40 years I've been sailing at sea. A war at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.85,1:21:31.86,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一场没有战役的战争  没有纪念碑\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A war with no battles. No monuments.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.03,1:21:35.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,只有死伤者\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Only casualties.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.82,1:21:42.79,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,妻子在结婚当日  变成寡妇\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I widowed her the day I married her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.91,1:21:49.46,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她去世的时候  我还在船上\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My wife died while I was at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.10,1:22:11.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,找人看守轮机舱\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Post guards in the engineering spaces.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.36,1:22:16.19,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,弄坏履带的人  会做出更严重的破坏\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If he can get to the caterpillar, he can get to somewhere more vital.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.11,1:22:21.93,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,钟斯  他在那里?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Where is he, Jonesy?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.93,1:22:24.74,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,目标在我们右舷\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Conn, Sonar. Target is now coming out of our starboard baffles.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.91,1:22:29.25,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他想回到原来的路线\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My read is that he's returning to base course.
