Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.30,1:22:40.34,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,等三十秒  然后取消静航\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Give him another 30 seconds. Then secure from silent running.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.51,1:22:45.14,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们收到讯息\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Captain, here's what we got on the ELF.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.10,1:22:49.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -不用谢  长官\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Thanks.  -Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.86,1:23:00.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是什么?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.86,1:23:03.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你绝对不相信\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're not going to believe this.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.25,1:23:18.42,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们要及早返航\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Commander, we're approaching no return.
