Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.76,1:23:22.99,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-我们要返航  -再等一会儿\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-We have to turn back.  -Give it a couple more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.99,1:23:25.22,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不行  燃料快不够了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Negative. Fuel status says we turn around now.
