Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.75,1:23:33.81,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但只有作战时才可动用\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I'm not allowed to invade that except during war.
