Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.99,2:04:00.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-钟斯  他在哪里?  -距离很近\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Where is he, Jonesy?  -Close, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.12,2:04:05.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-正前方900米  -终于找到了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-900 meters, directly ahead.  -Got him.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.79,2:04:08.96,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-校准后发射  -距离太近\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Mark bearings and fire.  -We are too close.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.12,2:04:14.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别争论  发射鱼雷\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't argue with me. Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.01,2:04:19.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,又发射了一颗鱼雷  它随时会爆炸\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Another torpedo. It went active the moment it was launched.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.63,2:04:24.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-左满舵  平衡舰首  -鱼雷锁定我们了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Left full rudder. Ease off on your bow planes.  -I think he's got us.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:34.36,2:04:37.78,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,达拉斯号  干得漂亮!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Way to go, Dallas!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:41.53,2:04:46.66,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,鱼雷在五百码外冲过来  你成功了\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Torpedo is in acquisition. Range 500 yards and closing. You've done it, Thompson!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.83,2:04:51.12,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,希望这行得通  大副  浮上水面\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I hope this works. All right, chief, put us on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.29,2:04:54.75,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,准备发射反鱼雷  听我命令  五  四...\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Countermeasure station, on my mark. 5, 4...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:57.46,2:05:02.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,发射反鱼雷  紧急上浮\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Release counter measures. Emergency blow. Full rise.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.77,2:05:13.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,500英尺\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}500 feet.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.52,2:05:16.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,快点上浮\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come on, Big D. Fly!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.79,2:05:39.46,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,鱼雷没停下来  它在寻找别的目标\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That torpedo is still active. It's searching for another target, now.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.70,2:06:09.91,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,竟然是他X的厨师\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A goddamn cook.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:32.73,2:06:35.85,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,它锁定我们了!\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Torpedo is locked on us!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:36.02,2:06:38.82,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-雅夫级潜艇离我们多近?  -左后方1000码处\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-How close is that Alfa, Jonesy?  -1,000 yards dead astern, going to port.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.82,2:06:41.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-反方向转  -遵命\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Reverse your turn.  -Aye,sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.07,2:06:51.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们冲向敌方  鱼雷跟着我们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're turning straight at him. Torpedo's still on our tail.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.21,2:07:00.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在适当的时候退开\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The hard part about playing chicken is knowing when to flinch.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:05.38,2:07:09.43,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,距离400码  350码  300码...\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Collision in 400 yards, 350, 300...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.60,2:07:15.31,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-舰长!  -右满舵  俯倾30度\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Captain!  -Right full rudder. 30 degree down angle.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.48,2:07:18.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这次必定很惊险\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This one's going to be close.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:21.86,2:07:25.61,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你个傲慢的傻瓜  你会害死我们\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You arrogant ass, you've killed us.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.97,2:07:57.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们确定了红十月号的位置\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We have ascertained the Red October's final position.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:57.73,2:08:00.69,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但爆炸碎片\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But...given the depth of the water and the spread of...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.69,2:08:03.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,遍布深海\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the wreckage spreads across a wide area...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:03.82,2:08:06.74,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们要花一段时间调查\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}it'll be some time before anything's recovered.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:06.90,2:08:09.72,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你们的人正在\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}However, your people are interviewing...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.72,2:08:12.53,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,安排船员回国\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the crew now and making arrangements for their return.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:12.70,2:08:17.04,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这是一场悲惨的意外  大使先生\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This has been a terrible tragedy, Mr. Ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:17.21,2:08:22.46,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果早点找我们  悲剧可能不会发生\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I can only stress hat if you'd come to us earlier, it might have been avoided.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.55,2:08:29.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-我欣赏你坦诚的性格  -彼此彼此\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-I appreciate your candor in the matter.  -And I yours, Andrei.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:32.22,2:08:35.06,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可能在将来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Perhaps in the future...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:35.06,2:08:37.89,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,会有更先进的科技来研究潜艇残骸\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the technology will be available for an investigation of the wreckage.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:38.06,2:08:41.94,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:46.23,2:08:52.62,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-还有一件事  我难以启齿...  -请说\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-There is another matter, one that I'm reluctant to...  -Please.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.12,2:09:01.21,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一艘雅夫级潜艇  曾经在大浅滩出没\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}One of our submarines, an Alfa, was last reported in the area of the Grand Banks.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:01.37,2:09:05.63,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,它跟我们失去联络\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We've not heard from her for some time.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:06.92,2:09:11.47,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,又一艘潜艇失踪?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Andrei. You've lost another submarine?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.87,2:09:23.27,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,缅因州  佩诺布斯科特河
Dialogue: 0,2:09:25.86,2:09:30.36,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,长途跋涉来  把潜艇藏在河里\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All this way to hide a submarine in a river.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:31.57,2:09:34.64,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这儿距离海军基地一百英里\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're 100 miles from the nearest naval base...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.64,2:09:37.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,而且卫星不会再窥探这地方\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}for the last place that satellites will ever look.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.20,2:09:43.08,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我在这里长大\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I grew up around here.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.25,2:09:48.59,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,祖父在那个岛教我钓鱼\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My grandfather taught me to fish off that island over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.63,2:09:58.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你心里还有一个疑问  为什么不问?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There is one question you haven't asked me yet. Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.39,2:10:03.73,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在适当的时候  你自然会说出来\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, I figured you would tell me when you were ready.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:06.65,2:10:11.28,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有人说  我们要主动攻打美国\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now, there are those who believe we should attack the United States first.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.44,2:10:17.95,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,了却一切恩怨  红十月号就是为此而建造的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Settle everything in one moment. Red October was built for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.12,2:10:23.67,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-然后  莫斯科会付出沉重的代价  -也许吧\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-When the dust settles from this, there's going to be hell to pay in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.83,2:10:27.04,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那可能是好事\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Maybe some good will come from it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:27.21,2:10:32.88,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一场小革命能整顿国家  你觉得呢?\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A little revolution now and then is a healthy thing, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:38.68,2:10:42.48,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你仍然喜欢钓鱼吗  瑞恩?  -是的\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}-Do you still like to fish, Ryan?  -Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.89,2:10:47.81,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,维尔纳斯有一条河  跟这里差不多\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's a river, not unlike this one, near Vilnius...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.98,2:10:52.65,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我祖父在那里教我钓鱼\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}where my grandfather taught me to fish.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.70,2:10:58.45,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,"大海为每个人带来新希望"\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"And the sea will grant each man new hope."
Dialogue: 0,2:10:58.62,2:11:02.33,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,"正如睡眠带来梦境"\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"As sleep brings dreams."
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.38,2:11:11.09,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,克里斯托弗  哥伦布\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Christopher Columbus.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:14.97,2:11:18.35,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,欢迎光临新世界  舰长\N{\fn方正综艺简体}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Welcome to the new world, sir.

